summary: it\'s a first player house across the riverwoods river.
descriptionHtml:
DESCRIPTION:
This is a Woody Place, just taste it and tell me what you think about it. the key it\'s in the first bandit camp (with the first treasure map.) Head directly south of those first few stone you pass by at the beginning of the game. You can take that first road south from those stones until you come to a sign on your right. Take a right at that sign and follow that road until you see the bandit camp on your left after a short walk.

Note: you can taste it using the console but first save your game!.
                             Code: coc myhouse1interior
author: blade316
